___________________________Bisogna autorizzare la JVM ad accettare SSL di gox :

Run the JVM with options : 

To generate the keystore containing the two certificares I used
 
 keytool -import -alias mtgox-data -file data.mtgox.com.cer -keystore mtgox.jks
 keytool -import -alias mtgox-com -file mtgox.com.cer -keystore mtgox.jks

Il file si trova in resources/ssl/mtgox.jks , password h4rdc0r_


